Revision history for Perl extension Hook::Scope.

0.04  Wed Jan  1 21:10:08 CET  2003
	- Preliminary support for the PRE {} statement.
	  Needs B::Generate and optimizer to work.
        - In next version POST {} will be compiletime,
	  and runtime, POST {} will be renamed leave {}

0.03  Sun Sep 22 13:01:59 CEST 2002
	- [rt.cpan.org:1197] Applied documentation patch from
	Elizabeth Mattijsen
	- Uses Module::Signature to verify module with my gpg key
	- Updated documentation to provide bug report email address	

0.02  Sun Jun  9 23:56:08 CEST 2002
	- Changed leave() to POST() after suggestion from
	Rafael Garcia-Suarez to be more compatible with Perl6 naming.

0.01  Sun Jun  9 10:13:36 2002
	- original version; created by h2xs 1.22 with options
		--skip-autoloader -b5.5.0 -g -c -f Hook::Scope

